    <lb n="13"/>τὰ ἐντάγια ἑαυτῶν τῆς ἑαυτῶν ἐσθῆ-

    <lb n="14"/>τος ἧς διαδεδώκασ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>ν <subst><add place="inline"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἤδ</unclear>η</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable"><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>δη</del></subst> ἐπὶ τῆς 

    <lb n="15"/>αὐτῆς Ἀλεξανδρέων καὶ τηρήσω παρ᾽ 

    <lb n="16"/>ἐμαυτ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ῦ <choice><corr>μέχρι</corr><sic>μεχρις</sic></choice> Ἀλε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ξ</supplied>ανδρείας <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.209">ἢ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἀ</unclear>πο-

